fields.name: Epomaker Urban
fields.description: The Epomaker Urban keycap set features a 133-key layout with Cherry profile, made from durable PBT material. These keycaps support RGB shine through and are perfect for ANSI layouts.

fields.name: Epomaker Alice Adventure
fields.description: The Epomaker Alice Adventure keycap set supports both ANSI and ISO layouts with a 156-key count. Featuring a Cherry profile, these keycaps are made from PBT material and do not support RGB shine through.

fields.name: Epomaker Peach
fields.description: The Epomaker Peach keycap set features a 133-key ANSI layout with OEM profile. Made from durable PBT material, these keycaps support RGB shine through.

fields.name: Epomaker Mossy
fields.description: The Epomaker Mossy keycap set features a 133-key ANSI layout with Cherry profile. Made from durable PBT material, these keycaps do not support RGB shine through.

fields.name: KiiBOOM Ice Cream
fields.description: The KiiBOOM Ice Cream keycap set features a 132-key ANSI layout with MOA profile. Made from durable PBT material, these keycaps do not support RGB shine through.

fields.name: Akko Neon Keycap Set
fields.description: The Akko Neon keycap set features a striking neon color scheme with a 157-key count, Cherry profile, and PBT material. It supports both ANSI and ISO layouts and includes additional novelties.

fields.name: Akko London Keycap Set
fields.description: The Akko London keycap set features a stylish London theme with a 158-key count, Cherry profile, and PBT material. It supports both ANSI and ISO layouts and includes additional novelties.

fields.name: KiiBOOM Graffiti Keycap Set
fields.description: The KiiBOOM Graffiti keycap set features a vibrant graffiti design with a 129-key count, Cherry profile, and PBT material. It supports ANSI layouts and includes additional novelties.

fields.name: Epomaker IFLOAT Keycap Set
fields.description: The Epomaker IFLOAT keycap set features a pastel color scheme with a 131-key count, Cherry profile, and PBT material. It supports ANSI layouts and includes additional novelties.

fields.name: Epomaker Sea Sailor Keycap Set
fields.description: The Epomaker Sea Sailor keycap set features a nautical theme with a 137-key count, Cherry profile, and PBT material. It supports both ANSI and ISO layouts and includes additional novelties.
